==English==
===Syllables===
[Ad-jec-tive] \Ad"jec*tive\

===Etymology===
Latin ''ad'' '''next to''' + ''-ject-'' perfect passive participle form of ''[[jacere]]'' '''throw''' + ''-ivus'' adjective ending

Meaning: word thrown next to a noun, modifying it.

===Noun===
'''adjective'''

# a "describing word", modifying a [[noun]] or [[pronoun]], for example ''big'' or ''heavy''

